Package: inops
Title: Infix Operators for Detection, Subsetting and Replacement
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Antoine", "Fabri", email = "antoine.fabri@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Karolis", "Koncevi\u00e7ius", email = "karolis.koncevicius@gmail.com", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides infix operators to detect, subset, and replace the elements matched by a given condition.
  The functions have several variants of operator types, including subsets, ranges, regular expressions and others.
  Implemented operators work on vectors, matrices, and lists.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0),
    purrr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
